				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Problems levelling from 12-16 ? You need to get to the Lavastorm Mountains zone. This is the best kept soloing secret in Norrath - frequently i go to this zone during prime time and there are fewer than 10 people in it. At lvl 12-14 you will find Fire Drakes a-plenty which generally con blue, don't group, dont't aggro AND have good loot. About 1 in 5 or 10 will drop lower end gems (onyx, carnelian, rose quartz), which is great for apprentice jewellers. You coudn't ask for better prey. At level 14 and up, you can solo fire imps, which give great XP and have pretty good loot. Make sure to cast &quot;cancel magic&quot; on the imps to take our their fire shields, otherwise you and your pet will die swiftly.<BR>
<BR>
  Gilauran<BR>
  12, no 13, no 14 HE Chanter<BR>
  Tholluxe Paells server
